# TraceQL Examples

These examples target service `{{ service_name }}` in namespace `{{ app.namespace }}`.

TraceQL attributes depend on the real instrumentation. If a query returns no data, inspect the trace attributes available in Grafana Explore and adapt the selectors.

## Traces For The Service

```traceql
{ resource.service.name = "{{ service_name }}" }
```

## Traces For The Service And Namespace

```traceql
{ resource.service.name = "{{ service_name }}" && resource.k8s.namespace.name = "{{ app.namespace }}" }
```

## Route Filter

```traceql
{ span.http.route = "/weather" }
```

## GET Requests

```traceql
{ span.http.method = "GET" }
```

## Server Errors

```traceql
{ span.http.status_code >= 500 }
```
